447
00:40:32,100 --> 00:40:35,180
Do you really think my family isn't involved in the matter now?

448
00:40:36,410 --> 00:40:37,640
I'm really sorry.

449
00:40:37,640 --> 00:40:41,870
Don't you know how serious it is to kill an army officer?

450
00:40:44,440 --> 00:40:46,320
I know.

451
00:40:47,470 --> 00:40:50,310
You'd rather sacrifice yourself

452
00:40:50,310 --> 00:40:53,050
than get him in danger, right?

453
00:40:56,890 --> 00:40:59,030
Talk to me!

454
00:40:59,980 --> 00:41:04,310
Third Brother, I have nothing to say.

455
00:41:05,180 --> 00:41:07,860
I've told you.

456
00:41:07,860 --> 00:41:12,430
I will take all of the responsibility for the matter.

457
00:41:23,130 --> 00:41:25,270
Lin Hangjing.

458
00:41:26,100 --> 00:41:28,830
Do you really think...

459
00:41:28,830 --> 00:41:31,860
