460
00:41:33,620 --> 00:41:35,860
Do you believe I would repeat that day

461
00:41:35,860 --> 00:41:39,480
and put a bullet into his head?

462
00:41:40,730 --> 00:41:42,890
You won't.

463
00:41:44,950 --> 00:41:49,940
Or you would have killed him.

464
00:41:52,030 --> 00:41:54,850
Do you think you really know me?

465
00:41:56,590 --> 00:41:59,950
He is my enemy.

466
00:41:59,950 --> 00:42:02,590
I will kill him.

467
00:42:02,590 --> 00:42:06,130
No one in Beixin City can stop me.

468
00:42:06,130 --> 00:42:08,400
No one can stop you.

469
00:42:09,980 --> 00:42:14,330
But Third Brother, I trust you.

